Subject: [PATCH 21/22] =?UTF-8?q?feat:=20v0.2=20T2a=20=E2=80=94=20withDecl?=
 =?UTF-8?q?NameForAuxNaming=20so=20tactic-extracted=20aux=20proofs=20land?=
 =?UTF-8?q?=20under=20the=20async=20prefix;=20re-enable=20under-context=20?=
 =?UTF-8?q?by-proofs?=
